foia:AppealResponseTimeSection.foia:FootnoteText: Due to its decentralized program, DoD is unable to calculate an Agency Overall Median. The numbers for this section are the average of each column.

foia:InformationGrantedResponseTimeSecti.foia:FootnoteText: Due to its decentralized program, DoD is unable to calculate an Agency Overall Median. The numbers for this section are the average of each column. Due to system limitations the chart in this section may contain information about unperfected requests for some DoD components.

foia:SimpleResponseTimeIncrementsSection.foia:FootnoteText: The charts in this section may not reflect all perfected requests that were processed for some of DoD components. DoD is taking steps to ensure that all requests are properly categorized moving forward. Due to system limitations, the chart in this section may contain information about unperfected requests for some DoD components.

Due to system limitations, the chart in this section may contain information about unperfected requests for some DoD components.

foia:ExpeditedProcessingSection.foia:FootnoteText: Due to its decentralized program, DoD is unable to calculae Agency Overall medians. The Number Granted, Number Denied, and Number Adjudicated Within Ten Days are the sum total of the column, while the Median and Average are the average of the column.

foia:FeeWaiverSection.foia:FootnoteText: Due to its decentralized program, DoD is unable to calculate Agency Overall medians. The Granted and Denied columns are the sum total of each column, while the Median and Average are the average of the column.
